ğŸ”¹ 1ï¸âƒ£ Adjacency Matrix

For graph with n vertices:

n Ã— n matrix

A[i][j] = 1 if edge exists, else 0

For undirected graph:

Matrix is symmetric.

For simple graph:

Diagonal entries = 0.

